{"tid":2141600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[難打醬打瀉醬]東風軍車貪污案，5000架裝甲車用廢鐵製造，中國軍隊能打仗？","createTime":"2020-08-05T22:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T12:01:58.000Z","uid":26770,"like":75,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"9d857b2b7883aa565f14d2243dafe3a83e7ca505","tid":2141600,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T22:19:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fWUAJm4CUwY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfWUAJm4CUwY&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2Fz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=2a227ab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fWUAJm4CUwY</a><br />\n8.6【冰山一角】東風軍車貪污案，5000架裝甲車用廢鐵製造，中國軍隊能打仗？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6e478a91d3b9ec8578243819f260ad417983af","tid":2141600,"uid":26770,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T22:21:19.000Z","msg":"文字<br />\n【豆腐渣軍車】傳用劣質鋼令官兵傷亡 東風汽車特種裝備部2高層落馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200806/J65NCGXCV6XCQ5DB55XM2AVXWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200806%2FJ65NCGXCV6XCQ5DB55XM2AVXWI%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2Fz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=1ec94835\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200806%2FJ65NCGXCV6XCQ5DB55XM2AVXWI%2F&h=9c2518ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200806/J65NCGXCV6XCQ5DB55XM2AVXWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n中印邊境六月爆發衝突，導致43死傷，震驚中外。事隔近兩個月，內地網絡瘋傳中方軍車製造商<strong>東風汽車</strong>的特種裝備部門兩名高層，因為受賄採購<strong>劣質鋼材作原材料，令中國軍人傷亡而落馬</strong>。軍事評論員黃東稱，認為這次事件可信，事件亦顯示軍方弊案的冰山一角。資深時事評論員劉銳紹指出，事件涉發軍方機密，難以求證，要多加觀察才可斷定高層落馬與中印邊境衝突有關。"},{"pid":"2647b54d40232e8618718f9aba3ce63cc2cdba5c","tid":2141600,"uid":200083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T22:23:43.000Z","m